title: 560: Rob Dionne of the  Open Sky Fitness Podcast
description: In this episode Sal, Adam & Justin interview Rob Dionne of the Open Sky Fitness Podcast (www.openskyfitness.com). In this episode Sal, Adam and Justin talk with Rob about his acting career, the fitness business and achieving success in the industry.
